&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;    By default, MariaDB comes with a database named &amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;test&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39; that anyone can
